  "name": "Nagaraja COU1 — Non-cannulated pedicle screw compression-bending credibility assessment (Minimal Profile)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for FEA prediction of ASTM F1717 static compression-bending performance of a non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw construct evaluated under ASME V&V 40-2018. The intended use is prediction of construct stiffness and load-to-failure for a Class II spinal fixation device in the lumbar spine under static compressive-bending loads as defined in ASTM F1717. The FEA model ensemble (FDA, Ansys, DePuy Synthes) is compared against N=11 experimental constructs across two laboratories. All 13 V&V 40 factors assessed; one factor (Test conditions) is below required level due to single test condition. Conformance is declared under ProfileMinimal; structured hasContextOfUse linkage is intentionally absent per this profile tier.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/nagaraja-f1717-compression-bending-req-001",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/nagaraja-fea-f1717-static-compression-bending-claim-001",
